name: Gameoflife
body:
### Info
Enjoy Conway's Game of Life written in Java. It took me a while to write (like 9ish hours because I am still learning but I think I did alright). Check it out. Download it, open up the package in a compiler like BlueJ, and run the Main class and its main method. Enjoy :D
